he other hand, I'm hoping he was just a highly disappointed cleric since he too was working on his Aegis and had more waiting ahead of him.<br><br>Anyhow, good luck to all.  This thing ROCKS  (even though I'm glad I never have to kill another bandit for a sash as long as I live ROFL).  This is the best feeling I have EVER had in EQ - even better than making level 50.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
